#. Id: 1534558-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (1534557-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Talk to valamon
#: 1534558-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Welcome to Ark... welcome to revolution! Here, you'll fight when I tell you, wear what I tell you, eat, bleed, piss when I tell you. But when you die a hero, in a pool of your own blood on the battlefield with the noble lords, you'll appreciate that your life was not wasted like all those other nobodies of the world... Those who die for nothing, who die like dogs..."
msgstr "歡迎來到方舟......歡迎來到革命！在這裡，當我告訴你時，你會打架，當我告訴你時，穿我告訴你的，吃飯，流血，小便。但是當你死去的英雄，在戰場上與貴族領主的血泊中，你會明白你的生活並沒有像世界上所有其他無名者一樣浪費......那些一無所有的人，誰像狗一樣死..."

#. Id: 1534559-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (1534558-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Talk to valamon
#: 1534559-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "You'll die as a brotherhood, as part of a revolution to take DOWN those very lords... Because we are not dogs!"
msgstr "你將作為一個兄弟會而死，作為一場革命的一部分，讓那些領主們走下去......因為我們不是狗！"

#. Id: 1534560-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (1534559-Dialogue.mod)
